name: VirtualBackgroundSourceStateReason
description:
The reason why virtual background is not successfully enabled.
Since
                    v3.5.0

parameters.Success: 0: The virtual background is successfully enabled.

parameters.ImageNotExist: 1: The custom background image does not exist. Please check the value of source in VirtualBackgroundSource.

parameters.ColorFormatNotSupported: 2: The color format of the custom background image is invalid. Please check the value of color in VirtualBackgroundSource.

parameters.DeviceNotSupported: 3: The device does not support using the virtual background.
